---
---

<link
  href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Zilla+Slab:wght@400;700&display=swap"
  rel="stylesheet"
/>

<div class="hero-section">
  <div class="img-wrapper">
    <img
      src="https://ik.imagekit.io/mbccqjudb/donate%20page/donatepagehero.png"
      alt="Donate to Nepal Climate Hub"
    />
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section-container">
  <div class="donate-content">
    <div class="donate-banner">
      <p class="donate-text">Donate us</p>
    </div>
    <div class="donate-layout">
      <div class="donate-text-column">
        <h1 class="donate-heading">
          Donate to Nepal Climate Hub
        </h1>

        <p class="donate-paragraph">
          Nepal is already facing the impacts of climate change. Many young
          people want to act but lack access to clear information, networks, and
          real opportunities to get involved.
        </p>

        <p class="donate-paragraph">
          Nepal Climate Hub is a registered, youth-led nonprofit working to
          change that. We educate, connect, and empower youth across Nepal to
          take informed, meaningful climate action.
        </p>

        <p class="donate-paragraph">
          NCH is run by volunteers who are also full-time students and young
          professionals. We’ve built and sustained this work by contributing our
          own time and covering many costs ourselves. As we grow, your support
          helps young people turn climate concern into action, while keeping NCH
          free, accessible and sustainable for youth across Nepal.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="donate-image-column">
        <img
          src="https://ik.imagekit.io/mbccqjudb/donate%20page/Team%20NCH%201.png"
          alt="Team Nepal Climate Hub"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .section-container {
    font-family: Roboto;
  }

  .hero-section {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .img-wrapper {
    width: 100%;
    height: 416px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .img-wrapper img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .donate-banner {
    padding: 2px 14px;
    position: absolute;
    background-color: #cefe00;
    transform: rotate(-3deg);
    top: -20px;
    left: 0px;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .donate-text {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #000;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .donate-content {
    max-width: 1280px;
    padding: 3rem 0px 4rem;
    position: relative;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .donate-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.9fr) minmax(0, 1.1fr);
    align-items: center;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .donate-text-column {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .donate-image-column img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .donate-heading {
    font-size: 30px;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: #000;
    font-family: "Zilla Slab", serif;
    font-weight: bold;
    line-height: 36px;
  }

  .donate-paragraph {
    line-height: 24px;
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: #333;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 1280px) {
    .donate-content {
      margin: 0px 48px;
    }

    .donate-layout {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.9fr) minmax(0, 1.1fr);
      gap: 28px;
    }

    .donate-image-column {
      justify-self: end;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .donate-content {
      padding: 2rem 0px;
      margin: 0px 24px;
    }

    .donate-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .donate-image-column {
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .donate-heading {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>

